{"tid":228164,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[報已上]小心補習中介Hottutor 陰招，多收中介費兼無限期拖欠","createTime":"2017-05-03T16:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T14:52:48.000Z","uid":7775,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f6f5492a9eda6f2749bbd9989b9ae0cb64d6bd70","tid":228164,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:36:30.000Z","msg":"之前小弟跟進過Hottutor 單野<br />\n<br />\n事隔一排，中介狗以為無咗下文，狙擊行動爛尾之際<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_507039_0&amp;i=20170504/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_507039_0%26i%3D20170504%2F&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVETPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d59647d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_507039_0%26i%3D20170504%2F&h=8bf4fd17\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_507039_0&amp;i=20170504/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_507055_0&amp;i=20170504/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_507055_0%26i%3D20170504%2F&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVETPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=307e573e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_507055_0%26i%3D20170504%2F&h=0ad18f0e\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_507055_0&amp;i=20170504/</a><br />\n<br />\n相關Facebook貼文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hugegod/posts/805747749576975/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhugegod%2Fposts%2F805747749576975%2F&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVETPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=2450ad6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hugegod/posts/805747749576975/</a><br />\n<br />\n狙擊行動繼續，下一步集合投訴人搵議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa619e91a7a4cf2cde38726e5172e4cfa985c7b4","tid":228164,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/04/003728_f05352e5f69210af957e49348900bd93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F04%2F003728_f05352e5f69210af957e49348900bd93.jpg&h=d39f3a6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開業15年，再一次獲得壹週刊專題報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fea1d229e97181cd9a219eb7bc6b9cc98d6ce3a","tid":228164,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:41:59.000Z","msg":"「其實都沒什麼辦法追討，因為都沒有該公司地址，打電話又不通，短訊又不回覆，所以都沒什麼機會追到，追到的機會都頗渺茫。」近日，有網民在討論區出帖文，投訴被一間名叫Hot Tutor（熱誠補習）的補習介紹中心，拖欠多付了的中介費，引起熱烈討論，因為很多人都被該中心拖數。<br />\n<br />\n根舉該中心規定，補習導師要將首兩星期的補習收入作為中介費。例如每星期補兩堂，每堂200元，導師便要先付800元中介費。但有多名導師表示，補了一堂後家長便停止僱用，介紹中心表示，這種情況中介費只需頭一堂收入的一半，並承諾40天內會退還多付了的中介費，但遲遲沒有兌現，而受害者多是想賺點生活費的大學生。"},{"pid":"47b23787109b72142cdc81f9aad181accdcfdfe4","tid":228164,"uid":90127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:43:11.000Z","msg":"其實攪番個網上平台免中介費配對補習係真係有得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558b09182bf447ef4b36c4193e1015442e3e7d96","tid":228164,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:46:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實攪番個網上平台免中介費配對補習係真係有得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收中介費本身無問題<br />\nit狗都要食飯<br />\n<br />\n重點係巧立名目呃人就唔得"},{"pid":"f305291b2b7e869f1676ccca1b8ae3b0c1df757b","tid":228164,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:51:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">補習中介狗 要脅公佈事主資料</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96v2AnH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn